name:                bcbs-crawl
version:             0.2.0.0
synopsis:            This package contains an executable programm 'BcbsCrawler' that searches the web site of the BCBS (Basel Committee for Banking Supervision) at www.bis.org/bcbs for any type of publication. The program then saves the accompanying pdf files on disc and further information about the publications in a MongoDB database.
